mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Datebook", "On the Record and Record Report", "Feature Fashion", "As I See It", "Teen Directory", "Reunion", "The Dancers Walk-Thru", "Teaching Square Dancing", "Double the Dancers in Denver", "Ladies on the Square", "Interview: Marshall Flippo", "Style Series: Comfort-It's as Simple as That", "Canadian Promotion", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "SIO Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Johnny Davidson", "Paging the Round Dancers: Don and Donna Teufel", and "Experimental Lab: Workshop Ideas".
